Text: Hi Bruce, this is Steve. SleepNumber. Providing you my cell number so we can coordinate meeting up.

The address is:

3 Hedgerow Lane
Wayne, Pa
Steve, I got a guy to help me load the bed onto the trailer. does Friday around noon work for you? Bruce
OK then. Pete and I will see you at 3 Hedgerow Ln. at 12 noon on Friday the 21st. Bruce
Great. I’ll be there. Let’s text Thursday evening to confirm
Steve,  after speaking with my wife I was wondering if I could meet you at the house in Wayne at 10:30 am rather than 12 noon. does that still work for you?  Bruce
Yes that will work. See you then
Steve, I’m planning to be at the Wayne location between 1030 and 11. Is that still good for you? Bruce
I’ll get there an hour early and try and deflate the mattress
The bed works as advertised thank you so much Steve
Awesome! I’m very happy to hear this. Enjoy.
